{"tid":2334171,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：極權需要世人參與，才可以實現。","createTime":"2020-12-21T03:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T16:29:47.000Z","uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"423b634c77edfc4ae9a061735ed055266ed99f91","tid":2334171,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:56:37.000Z","msg":"陳雲：星期一講道，佛陀獅子吼。極權在世間，不離世間覺。離世覓極權，猶如尋兔角。<br />\n極權需要世人參與，才可以實現。昨日，香港很多人參與所謂通緝並且成功舉報，協助差役在旺角捕捉了人權鬥士、病人權利維護者李運強。<br />\n追查一個感冒患者（即是曾經和不斷會感冒的你），政府外判了極權的工序，香港人樂意參與。<br />\n<br />\n去年死了的人？在深圳扣押的十二個義士？給共產黨的社會工程學克服了。<br />\n<br />\n香港人既然憎恨陳雲，就無須同共產黨鬥，乾脆投降啦。底牌都被看到了，還扮嘢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a7f1a8b4a0f6982d091087d64e1f5b6d199d00","tid":2334171,"uid":41873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4nYieGZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4nYieGZ.png&h=addc2753&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o8utBVk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo8utBVk.png&h=4b843d42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JHZ9mm1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJHZ9mm1.png&h=191aae4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2c2beef6c15b4e88f512a041645d7854875b6cc","tid":2334171,"uid":197783,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T04:29:04.000Z","msg":"陳雲老師，有交差餉有交稅的話，算唔算係支持極權呢？ <br />\n<br />\n守燈號過班馬線，又算唔算參與了極權？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求老師指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d763ccda7ada90622fcfb65c8780c037e67787cd","tid":2334171,"uid":281735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:29:47.000Z","msg":"收皮啦陳匪雲根，自己不學無術混淆視聽仲成日老屈人支持政府乜乜乜，根本個